{"tid":1135170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3行山友飛鵝山報警稱俾狼圍","createTime":"2019-05-02T06:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T07:05:18.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa27d8cc53529fa2041d99eafdb7ad89080c5e5","tid":1135170,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSxgUNa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSxgUNa.png&h=64a521de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AHpjdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AHpjdR.png&h=55bc6c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自廣州的大學生劉小姐（右）和黃小姐懷疑行山人士，誤將野豬當是狼。翁鈺輝攝<br />\n<br />\n【2/5 13:40】新增內容<br />\n<br />\n飛鵝山基維爾營地出現狼蹤？晚上9時許，一名姓王22歲內地男子，與兩名內地友人來港行山，經過麥理浩徑第五段基維爾營地附近時，發現四隻類似狼的動物在草叢內徘徊，眾人擔心有危險不敢前行，於是由王報警求救。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場尋獲三人，他們沒有受傷，但沒有發現狼的下落，也沒有發現任何動物。警方將案列雜項處理。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》翻查資料，12年曾有行山人士行經基維爾營地時，亦遇到一頭身型龐大的動物（ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2UOul52），形態威武，不似普通流浪狗，警員到場發現原來是俄羅斯高加索犬，市面出售動輒過萬元。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2UOul52%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%85%8B%E5%A8%81%E6%AD%A6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%BC%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AA%E7%8B%97%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%AB%98%E5%8A%A0%E7%B4%A2%E7%8A%AC%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E9%9D%A2%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%92%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E3%80%82&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=b48f24c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2UOul52），形態威武，不似普通流浪狗，警員到場發現原來是俄羅斯高加索犬，市面出售動輒過萬元。</a><br />\n<br />\n早上《蘋果》記者再到飛鵝山了解情況，只見數隻大大小小的野豬，卻沒見狼蹤。<br />\n<br />\n來自廣州的兩名女大學生，今日到來行山。她們指有中港合拍的電影在此取景，因此到來一遊。對於有內地人報稱見到疑似犲狼，她們都表示驚訝，但認為有可能看錯。「有可能（夜晚）睇錯吧！冇聽過香港有狼，係有野豬。」<br />\n<br />\n她們表示會選在白天行山，要是遇到野豬，也會避在一旁，相信不會遭襲擊。"},{"pid":"fa9d04f9bb704d351b7e34b01138cf0da38a7cee","tid":1135170,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:53:32.000Z","msg":"內地"},{"pid":"a1f350aa7edff912a0a9249b55af0ee7a72a2938","tid":1135170,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"350"},{"pid":"7f8b5dc872dbe5407ba4d7295f808750e716becb","tid":1135170,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30c22ed999e5df3bbe295c6855da4579e069f63a","tid":1135170,"uid":47023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:18.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25a314f143ffd7572d0d8310cb5d9b09f49adc7","tid":1135170,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36ab4dcc261925d78b78770c2f1f9d081605db99","tid":1135170,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f21a5cd78896fc86d76327be6409cddd981f4a15","tid":1135170,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"鄰國啲學校無教狗同狼點分?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}